+		/*
+		 * When leaf 0BH or 1FH is defined, CL is pass-through
+		 * and EDX is always the x2APIC ID, even for undefined
+		 * subleaves. Index 1 will exist iff the leaf is
+		 * implemented, so we pass through CL iff leaf 1
